C     10/8/80 - MEORD SWITCH ADDED - S.P.
C     6/28/81 - NFIRSTOF, BLOCKRELATIVE KEYWORDS - S.P.
C     7/16/81 - KFRMTP FOR FORMFACTOR - FORMDERI, FORMASIS - S.P.
C     9/17/81 - LEBACK ADDED - S.P.
C     10/27/81 - BETAP, BETAT, WRITEWAV, WRITEITE KEYWORDS - S.P.
C     5/3/82 - SET MAXLF=0 AFTER CLEAR FOR LOG TABLE - S.P.
C     6/26/82 - ADD RELATIVISTIC AND SAVESITER SWITCHES - S.P.
C     6/10/83 - BREAK SWTWRD IN 2 PIECES FOR CDC - S.P.
C     8/16/83 - ADD ALIAI FOR MAXITERA, TRANSITIONS - S.P.
C     8/9/84 - MORE SAVESITERATION KEYWORDS - S.P.                       8240   
C     12/19/84 - ADD SIPOTENT KEYWORD - S.P.
C
C
C
C     IN THE FOLLOWING COMMON BLOCKS, VARIABLE NAMES OF THE FORM
C       D$$$$N  OR  I$$$$N
